    return dec_result

    while queue:
        newq_1 = queue.popleft()
        color = 0

        for nex in G[newq_1]:

            E[np.min(np.array([newq_1, nex])), max(newq_1, nex)] = color
            queue.append(nex)
        K = max(K, color)
    return K
